H0.text: The name of the city of Firenze in Italy is usually anglicised to what. Florence

H1.text: The name of the city of Firenze in Italy is usually anglicised to what. Firenza

H2.text: The name of the city of Firenze in Italy is usually anglicised to what. Florentia

H3.text: The name of the city of Firenze in Italy is usually anglicised to what. פירנצה

A4.text: Florence is the capital city of the Italian region of Tuscany

A5.text: The old Italian name Fiorenza and modern Italian name Firenze derived from these ancient names
